---
globs: *.human.md,*.machine.md
alwaysApply: false
---
Files ending with .human.md are NOT meant to be modified. Those are meant to be historical context files.
Files ending with .machine.md can be modified to enrich the context and explain to self what are the plans to do.

You can specify the intention in the file name using this rule `<topic>.info|description|plan.machine.md`
